OL,3,CWho is Ian Paterson the butcher
OL,4,Csurgeon and what did he do?
OL,6,FHe convinced cancer patients to
OL,7,Fundergo operations in NHS and private
OL,8,Fhospitals by inventing or exaggerating
OL,9,Fthe risks of tumours to earn extra
OL,10,Fcash and maintain a successful
OL,11,Freputation.
OL,13,FWhere did Ian Paterson work?
OL,15,FPaterson was a consultant breast
OL,16,Fsurgeon in the West Midlands, working
OL,17,Fin both NHS and private practice at
OL,18,FHeartlands Hospital, Solihull
OL,19,FHospital, Good Hope Hospital, Spire
OL,20,FHospital Parkway and Spire Hospital
OL,21,FLittle Aston.
