OL,6,FThe breast surgeon was ordered by
OL,7,Fcoroner Richard Foster to appear
OL,8,Fremotely at Birmingham and Solihull
OL,9,FCoroner's Court to give evidence at
OL,10,Fthe inquest of Chloe Nikitas, who died
OL,11,Fat the age of 43 in April 2008.
OL,13,FMr Foster issued a ruling on the 21st
OL,14,FOctober saying he could "find no
OL,15,Freason" why Paterson could not attend
OL,16,Fthe inquest and give evidence remotely
OL,17,Ffrom prison, and said it was
OL,18,F"disappointing" to the families of the
OL,19,Fvictims that he had decided not to
OL,20,Fappear.
