OL,7,Fand she died at the age of 43 at the
OL,8,FPriory Hospital in April 2008.
OL,10,FThe inquest into the death of Ms
OL,11,FNikitas is the first of 62 into the
OL,12,Fdeaths of Paterson's former patients
OL,13,Fscheduled to be heard at Birmingham
OL,14,Fand Solihull Coroner's Court over the
OL,15,Fnext eight months.
