OL,6,FThe second inquest into the death of
OL,7,Fanother of Paterson's victims opened
OL,8,Fon the 29th of October.
OL,10,FElaine Turbill, who was 63 and from
OL,11,FSolihull, was diagnosed with breast
OL,12,Fcancer and had a mastectomy carried
OL,13,Fout by Paterson the following month.
OL,15,FThe inquest in Birmingham heard that
OL,16,FElaine, who worked as a legal
OL,17,Fsecretary, had been married for 40
OL,18,Fyears and had two children.
